Package: sleepcycles
Title: Detection and Visualization of Sleep Cycles from Hypnogram Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jason", "Dude", , "jasondude16@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1783-7224"))
Description: The sleepcycles package provides tools for detecting, analyzing, and visualizing sleep cycles from hypnogram data using density-based and rule-based (Feinberg) algorithms. It supports both single-subject and grouped datasets, enabling users to extract and explore Non-REM (NREMP) and REM (REMP) periods with flexible parameter settings. The package includes interactive Shiny applications, a suite of visualization functions and utilities for preprocessing and validating sleep staging data. 
